'''Veterned''' was the capital city of [[Troiken/Legends|Troiken]]. Notable residents included [[Niai Fieso]] and [[Freon Drevan]].

==Behind the scenes==
The city Veterned was first identified in the [[Databank (original)|Databank]] by [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|''Hyperspace'']] member "exarxan" ([[Sander de Lange]]), who named it after his place of birth and living, [[Wikipedia:Deventer|Deventer]].

